Toko Buku Jongnam

00:12:36.383 --> 00:12:37.676
Hyeju.

00:12:37.968 --> 00:12:39.136
Kau datang.

00:12:40.304 --> 00:12:41.889
Apa <i>Bayangan Penjahat</i> sudah ada?

00:12:42.723 --> 00:12:43.724
Ya.

00:12:46.852 --> 00:12:47.853
Ini.

